  "title": "Today we are officially graduating with a Bachelor of Science in Comp...",
  "description": "Today we are officially graduating with a Bachelor of Science in Computer Science, concentration in Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning, minor in Mathematics from Florida Southern College. Perfect 4.0 GPA. University Honors. Three years. I say we because Shelly was there for every late night, every big moment, every step of the way. She came into my life when it was hardest, after I lost my first senior dog, Stormy, two years in. Stormy helped me start. Shelly finished it with me. I had people in my corner who showed up in ways I will never fully be able to put into words. None of this was mine alone. So to my dogs, my family, and my friends, we did it. Along the way I expanded my business, wrote a thesis, and became someone I am really proud of. I came in with a dream. I'm leaving with a fire that nothing is going to put out. What's next? Stay tuned. @International Audience ❤️🐍 #rescuedog #college #graduation #dogs",
